Nigel Benn is a former super middleweight champion . 
  The 51-year-old joined in a playful pads session with Ricky Hatton at his Manchester gym . 
  Hatton is now a boxing trainer and could train Benn's son Conor at the 2016 Olympics . 
  Benn is back in the ring for the first time since his defeat to Chris Eubank . 
  The ‘Dark Destroyer’ won the WBO middleweight title . 
 